main_code_empty_note:
Koodhka "Main" waa madhan.

Isticmaal tifaftiraha "Visual code" si aad u soo saarto summadan:
- Ka fur qaybta "Barnaamijka" ka palette amarka ee bidixda
- Jiid block ka mid ah nooca "Main" ee goobta shaqada code muuqaalka
- Ku dar gudaha dhexdeeda blocks kood kale si aad u hirgaliso ficilada iyo macquulka barnaamijkan

Barnaamijka "Main" wuxuu noqon karaa mid gacanta lagu maamulo ama si toos ah loo bilaabo iyadoo lagu salaynayo xaaladaha ugu dambeyntii lagu bixiyay code Setup.
setup_code_empty_note:
Koodhka "Setup" waa madhan.

Isticmaal tifaftiraha "Visual code" si aad u soo saarto summadan:
- Ka fur qaybta "Barnaamijka" ka palette amarka ee bidixda
- Jiid block ka mid ah nooca "Setup" goobta shaqada code muuqaalka
- Ku dar gudaha gudaha baloogyada koodka kale si aad u go'aamiso shuruudaha kicin doona "Main" fulinta code

Xeerkan ayaa la qiimeeyaa mar kasta oo dhacdo cusub dhacdo iyo ugu yaraan hal mar daqiiqadii.
capture_commands_description: Ku dar dhammaan amarada gacanta lagu sameeyay barnaamijka.
